<div id="page2">
    <a id="h2p" class="smooth"></a>
    
    <div id="page2text">
      <p class="lead">How To Play</p>
      <div id="summary">
          <p>Void is an asteroid shooting game developed for cs252.  The object of void is to fly around the screen and shoot asteroids as they drift by.  If an asteroid hits your ship you will lose a life.  After all 3 lives are lost, the game is finished.  Powerups can be collected by flying your ship over a yellow powerup icon.</p>
          <br>
      </div>

      <table id="cont">
          <tr>
            <td id ="l" class="titles">Movement</td>
            <td id ="c" class="titles">Misc</td>
            <td id ="r" class="titles">Shooting</td>
        </tr>
        <td class="left">W: Move ship up</td>
        <td class="center">ESC: Pause</td>
        <td class="right">Up Arrow: Fire up</td> 
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="left">A: Move ship left</td>
        <td class="center">Q: Toggle HUD</td>
        <td class="right">Left Arrow: Fire left</td> 
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="left">S: Move ship down</td>
        <td class="center">Space: Use powerup</td>
        <td class="right">Down Arrow: Fire down</td> 
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="left">D: Move ship right</td>
        <td class="center"></td>
        <td class="right">Right Arrow: Fire right</td> 
    </tr>
</table>
